<div id='contact-144846'><span class='name'>Michael Smith</span><span class='send-message'><a href="/content/Contact/view/contactid/144846/display/detail/">Details</a></span></div> </div>
<div class='commentbox'>
Ran this river on Nov 10th with just 1 GENERATOR, it was completely worth it and quite fun. The<br/>
flat sections are a little scrapy but there are some new playspots that show up at low water and<br/>
devil shoals has a change to it. Make sure the 1 generator releases for at least 2 hours, 3 is<br/>
better. We out ran the water and had to wait for it to catch up to us, so pay attention to the<br/>
level and enjoy. </div>
</td>
